notes.author: Matt Byrd
notes.content: Rogelio's parole report indicated a full recovery and he is active in the community.

notes.author: Jen Buckhalter
notes.content: Ressie has been in and out of the criminal system, but I can't track a motive for an extortion crime.

notes.author: Dave McGuiness
notes.content: Bud has been dealing with alcohol issues after his release and could not have pulled off a crime this sophisticated in his drunken state.

notes.author: Bob Charleston
notes.content: Loy has moved out of the country.
